Now let me run SPARQL to understand the full picture of measurement terms   
  with is_about pointing to PR_ classes:

Bash: Run SPARQL to find all measurement terms with is_about PR_ classes
$ cd /home/runner/work/efo/efo/src/ontology && cat > /tmp/test-isabout-pr.
  sparql << 'EOF'                                                             
    prefix oio: <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#>               
    prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>                              
    prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>                      
    prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>                 
    prefix obo: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/>                             
                                                                              
    SELECT DISTINCT ?term ?term_label ?protein ?protein_label ?protein_comment
    WHERE {                                                                   
      ?term rdf:type owl:Class ;                                              
        rdfs:subClassOf+ <http://www.ebi.ac.uk/efo/EFO_0001444> ;             
        rdfs:subClassOf [ owl:onProperty obo:IAO_0000136 ;                    
                          owl:someValuesFrom ?protein ] .                     
      FILTER(isIRI(?term))                                                    
      FILTER(STRSTARTS(STR(?protein), "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PR_"))  
      OPTIONAL { ?term rdfs:label ?term_label . }                             
      OPTIONAL { ?protein rdfs:label ?protein_label . }                       
      OPTIONAL { ?protein rdfs:comment ?protein_comment . }                   
    }                                                                         
    ORDER BY ?term_label                                                      
    EOF                                                                       
    ../../bin/robot query --use-graphs true --catalog catalog-v001.xml --input
  efo-edit.owl --select /tmp/test-isabout-pr.sparql /tmp/isabout-pr-results.  
  tsv 2>&1 | tail -5                                                          
                                                                              
    <exited with exit code 0>

